Module FYPManager
Package entities

Class Request

java.lang.Object
entities.Request
Direct Known Subclasses:
AllocRequest, DeregRequest, TitleRequest, TransferRequest
public abstract class Request extends Object
This abstract class is the parent class of all requests. It contains the attributes and methods that are common to all requests.
